personas                    : 7 ACI .agents (agents/) — the emergents, rendered from canon (no fabrication)

the four natures of emergence (each emergent is tagged with one):
  natural    — the alien Defenders of Naju, and Earth
  ethereal   — the Corridors (the shoot-'em-up gauntlets of light)
  spiritual  — the Guardian's Charge (the sacred, sacrificial mission)
  electrical — Miria the Guardian (android), the Fighter (star-craft), the Arsenal

